name: Orbofi AI
description: Orbofi is a factory of multimodal and tradable AI agents, that empowers anyone to create functional and tokenized AI agents in less than 1 min. Orbofi currently hosts about 3 million + personified AI agents, making it one of the world's largest platforms of multimodal AI agents. Orbofi's mission is to be the infrastructure that produces AI agents that are autonomous, able to lead economies and communities, that can produce digital products, and that bring a net positive value to the world.
